WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 11=

02:05.260 --> 02:07.900
Looks like Master You
can't clear your name this time.

02:11.130 --> 02:13.570
My foster father devoted himself
to bringing the Mu Clan

02:14.010 --> 02:14.980
back to the Li Sect.

02:15.030 --> 02:16.260
He'd die for it without regret.

02:16.260 --> 02:17.100
I have been shaped by

02:17.410 --> 02:19.220
my foster father's words
since childhood.

02:19.220 --> 02:21.220
Always place the Mu Clan above all else.

02:21.350 --> 02:22.270
After my foster father

02:22.270 --> 02:23.980
was betrayed by that traitor Nie Zhe,

02:24.410 --> 02:26.010
I endured humiliation and hardship,

02:26.010 --> 02:26.980
and tangled with scum like

02:26.980 --> 02:28.340
Yu Huiyin and Xiong Qianjin.

02:28.980 --> 02:31.220
All to wait for Mr. Mu's return.

02:31.780 --> 02:32.690
Unexpectedly,

02:32.690 --> 02:33.890
heaven is just,

02:34.130 --> 02:35.450
and Mr. Mu, you're safe and sound.

02:37.380 --> 02:38.260
Now foster father

02:39.380 --> 02:41.450
can finally rest in peace.

02:42.980 --> 02:44.170
Last night, I heard

02:45.380 --> 02:47.220
someone threw
Elder Qiu's memorial tablet

02:48.100 --> 02:49.410
off the cliff.

02:51.980 --> 02:53.660
It must be that scoundrel Li Yi's doing.

02:53.660 --> 02:54.540
I never thought,

02:54.540 --> 02:56.170
he'd commit such a despicable,

02:56.170 --> 02:57.320
unforgivable act.

02:57.320 --> 02:58.220
Mr. Mu,

02:58.220 --> 02:59.410
you should've killed him right then.

02:59.610 --> 03:00.540
Torn him limb from limb.

03:14.010 --> 03:14.850
Enough.

03:15.340 --> 03:16.180
Get up.

03:17.690 --> 03:18.820
Mr. Mu.

03:18.820 --> 03:19.660
You Guanyue,

03:19.800 --> 03:22.130
you know the last person
who came within three steps of me?

03:22.500 --> 03:24.380
Their grave's already overgrown.

03:26.890 --> 03:29.220
I'm utterly loyal to you, Mr. Mu.

03:29.440 --> 03:30.780
Heaven and Earth can bear witness.

03:31.570 --> 03:33.260
If you have any use for me,

03:33.500 --> 03:34.340
I will surely

03:34.340 --> 03:35.570
serve you with all my heart,

03:36.010 --> 03:38.100
even unto death.

03:38.100 --> 03:38.940
Very well.

03:40.060 --> 03:41.100
Then I'll be counting on

03:41.380 --> 03:44.100
your talents from now on, Mr. You.

03:50.660 --> 03:51.500
Have some tea.

04:14.290 --> 04:15.450
Thank you, Mr. Mu.

04:25.170 --> 04:27.020
I've called you all here tonight

04:27.220 --> 04:29.540
because calamity looms,
and my future grows uncertain.

04:29.900 --> 04:31.220
I know you're all loyal,

04:31.460 --> 04:32.850
but I can't bear to
drag you down with me.

04:33.020 --> 04:33.900
After much thought,

04:34.050 --> 04:35.610
I've decided to divide all my savings

04:35.610 --> 04:37.170
among every single one of you.

04:37.370 --> 04:38.340
Take care, everyone.

04:39.050 --> 04:40.980
Master You, what's happening?

04:41.250 --> 04:43.540
Chief failed to ambush
the Six Sects of Beichen

04:43.980 --> 04:45.050
and fled in defeat.

04:45.250 --> 04:46.370
In a fury and shame,

04:46.370 --> 04:47.210
he actually...

04:47.700 --> 04:49.850
He ordered every altar to
capture innocent villagers

04:49.850 --> 04:51.490
to refine corpse slaves.

04:51.490 --> 04:53.050
- What?
- Corpse slaves?

04:53.700 --> 04:55.610
The art of refining a corpse slave

04:56.460 --> 04:57.660
is utterly vicious.

04:57.850 --> 04:59.050
If he dares do this,

04:59.460 --> 05:02.140
I'm afraid Heaven itself
will strike us down.

05:02.140 --> 05:04.490
Besides, if corpse slaves
return to the world,

05:04.490 --> 05:07.100
all Jianghu sects
will rise up against us.

05:07.370 --> 05:08.250
By then,

05:08.700 --> 05:11.580
there will surely be another bloodbath.

05:12.290 --> 05:14.930
I can't bear to let my brothers
die with me.

05:15.930 --> 05:17.730
After you take this gold and silver,

05:18.340 --> 05:19.900
just make your plans for the future.

05:20.340 --> 05:21.180
Plans?

05:21.720 --> 05:23.140
We, the old followers of Elder Qiu,

05:23.270 --> 05:24.980
have long been a thorn
in the Chief's side.

05:25.100 --> 05:26.170
If we're attacked,

05:26.340 --> 05:27.220
we'll be the first

05:27.220 --> 05:28.460
to be thrown to the wolves.

05:28.610 --> 05:29.450
Years ago,

05:29.580 --> 05:31.100
the former Chief Nie Hengcheng

05:31.610 --> 05:32.810
refined these corpse slaves

05:33.700 --> 05:35.340
and throw everyone into panic.

05:35.340 --> 05:36.580
Half the sect are casualties.

05:37.580 --> 05:38.420
And now,

05:38.850 --> 05:40.490
are we doomed to
repeat the same mistake?

05:41.850 --> 05:43.980
Those corpse slaves, that unnatural filth,

05:44.250 --> 05:46.490
were the Nie clan's doing
to eliminate their enemies.

05:46.700 --> 05:48.850
Sadly, none within the sect
could restrain the Nie clan.

05:49.260 --> 05:50.290
If Mr. Mu were still here...

05:50.290 --> 05:51.460
If Mr. Mu were alive,

05:51.460 --> 05:53.050
he'd never let the Chief
run amok like this!

05:53.810 --> 05:54.900
Don't call him Chief.

05:55.250 --> 05:56.140
That whole family

05:56.290 --> 05:58.290
are traitors who stole
the Mu clan's legacy!

05:58.290 --> 06:00.810
It's a pity Mr. Mu vanished long ago.

06:01.100 --> 06:04.340
Seems you all still hold
the Mu clan in high regard.

06:05.050 --> 06:05.890
If

06:06.900 --> 06:08.660
the Young Master returns safely,

06:09.580 --> 06:10.700
what will you do?

06:15.190 --> 06:16.700
You Guanyue,
Master of Qinglong Altar,

06:16.850 --> 06:18.580
bows to welcome Mr. Mu's return.

06:30.050 --> 06:30.930
W... What?

06:36.290 --> 06:37.130
Young Master.

06:37.620 --> 06:38.500
The Founder of Mu clan

06:39.290 --> 06:40.290
founded the Li Sect

06:40.750 --> 06:42.290
to detach from worldly affairs

06:42.850 --> 06:44.900
and have disciples aid one another

06:46.050 --> 06:47.290
and share honor and disgrace.

06:48.290 --> 06:49.490
But now, Nie Zhe

06:49.900 --> 06:51.220
acts against all principles.

06:51.340 --> 06:52.540
He's cruel and without virtue,

06:53.420 --> 06:54.930
ignoring the lives of fellow disciples

06:55.920 --> 06:57.370
and throwing the Li Sect into trouble.

06:58.290 --> 06:59.130
The Mu clan

07:00.730 --> 07:01.930
will never stand by!

07:04.140 --> 07:05.850
Those who do not wish to follow Mr. Mu

07:06.100 --> 07:07.730
may take the gold and leave on your own.

07:07.830 --> 07:09.220
Mr. Mu will not hold it against you.

07:11.290 --> 07:12.250
Th... this…

07:18.720 --> 07:20.540
My foster father's
death anniversary is near.

07:20.810 --> 07:23.700
Looks like Nie Zhe
is about to start another purge.

07:32.660 --> 07:34.810
Wipe out the traitor Nie
and restore the Mu clan!

07:36.140 --> 07:38.540
Wipe out the traitor Nie
and restore the Mu clan!

07:38.850 --> 07:41.250
Wipe out the traitor Nie
and restore the Mu clan!

07:41.540 --> 07:43.810
Wipe out the traitor Nie
and restore the Mu clan!

07:44.290 --> 07:46.700
Wipe out the traitor Nie
and restore the Mu clan!

07:46.980 --> 07:49.610
Wipe out the traitor Nie
and restore the Mu clan!

07:53.340 --> 07:54.780
He surrendered that fast?

07:56.540 --> 07:57.810
Looks like Mu Qingyan

07:58.340 --> 08:00.250
truly has some clever tactics.

08:04.050 --> 08:06.340
Seize that girl named Xing.

08:06.540 --> 08:08.290
I'll have big use for her soon.

08:09.340 --> 08:10.180
Yes.

08:16.020 --> 08:18.220
You Guanyue has always been
a smooth operator,

08:18.370 --> 08:20.020
currying favor with everyone.

08:21.220 --> 08:23.050
His surrender isn't surprising.

08:23.780 --> 08:24.900
But why would the others

08:25.410 --> 08:26.810
throw their lives away?

08:26.810 --> 08:27.660
Fengge.

08:30.700 --> 08:33.010
What do you think of Mu Qingyan?

08:33.770 --> 08:34.940
I can't see through him.

08:35.340 --> 08:36.690
When Mu Zhengming was still alive,

08:36.690 --> 08:37.610
he was just a young man.

08:38.030 --> 08:39.850
Every day he only read books
and grew flowers,

08:40.300 --> 08:41.650
seeming gentle and harmless.

08:41.980 --> 08:43.250
But after Mu Zhengming's death,

08:43.890 --> 08:45.820
he quickly rallied Elder Qiu's faction,

08:45.960 --> 08:47.010
stormed the Bliss Palace.

08:47.580 --> 08:48.650
He nearly killed the Chief.

08:51.340 --> 08:53.530
That was just over a year ago.

08:55.250 --> 08:56.090
Anyone

08:56.650 --> 08:58.460
who endured what he did

08:58.650 --> 09:00.300
would have fallen into the abyss.

09:00.580 --> 09:02.820
But he clawed his way out of hell.

09:04.420 --> 09:05.460
It proves

09:06.130 --> 09:07.890
he has something to rely on.

09:07.890 --> 09:09.300
I don't care what he's relying on.

09:09.650 --> 09:10.610
Like I said,

09:11.100 --> 09:11.980
if he comes,

09:12.100 --> 09:13.060
he dies.

09:22.790 --> 09:24.420
They've already taken
the Qinglong Altar.

09:26.130 --> 09:27.180
Never thought

09:27.890 --> 09:29.890
Mu Qingyan is actually pretty capable.

09:30.300 --> 09:31.610
Nie Zhe is such a useless fool.

09:31.980 --> 09:33.730
Honestly, that's not so bad.

09:33.850 --> 09:35.460
The two sides fight nonstop,

09:35.460 --> 09:36.580
draining each other dry,

09:36.580 --> 09:37.650
losing everything.

09:37.890 --> 09:38.730
Perfect.

09:38.980 --> 09:39.820
Dad.

09:40.980 --> 09:41.850
Right now

09:41.850 --> 09:43.220
the demon sect is tearing itself apart.

09:43.340 --> 09:45.770
Why don't we sneak into
the Hanhai Mountains

09:45.770 --> 09:47.100
and wipe them out in one fell swoop?

09:55.020 --> 09:55.940
Lingbo, you're valiant.

09:56.940 --> 09:57.780
Yuzhi.

09:58.820 --> 09:59.730
Master.

09:59.740 --> 10:01.060
What's your take on this?

10:01.740 --> 10:03.650
The Nie clan has held the demon sect
for decades.

10:05.030 --> 10:07.060
Nie Zhe is backed by
Nie Hengcheng's old followers.

10:07.060 --> 10:07.900
His foundation is solid.

10:08.100 --> 10:09.980
Mu Qingyan may have seized
the Qinglong Altar,

10:10.320 --> 10:12.530
but the scale of their internal strife
remains unknown.

10:12.940 --> 10:14.300
Until we get definite news,

10:15.130 --> 10:15.980
I think

10:16.300 --> 10:17.700
we should not act rashly.

10:17.940 --> 10:19.180
That makes sense.

10:20.770 --> 10:21.770
The Qinglong Altar,

10:22.010 --> 10:23.530
though the gateway of the demon sect,

10:24.130 --> 10:26.610
is weak in strength
and cannot stand alone.

10:26.610 --> 10:28.460
If Nie Zhe strikes with
overwhelming force,

10:28.980 --> 10:29.820
the Mu clan

10:30.180 --> 10:31.580
will likely be wiped out.

10:31.940 --> 10:32.780
And you guys

10:33.200 --> 10:34.980
don't just focus on
martial training all day.

10:35.460 --> 10:38.370
Take some time to
read more books like Yuzhi.

10:40.730 --> 10:41.570
Zhao,

10:43.610 --> 10:44.890
come walk with me.

10:57.650 --> 10:58.490
Zhao.

10:59.180 --> 11:01.460
I promised your aunt

11:01.890 --> 11:03.250
that as long as I live,

11:03.700 --> 11:05.180
I will keep you safe.

11:05.650 --> 11:07.980
This time, I was trapped by a villain,

11:08.740 --> 11:11.060
leaving you to go down
the mountain alone to find medicine.

11:11.610 --> 11:12.450
I have

11:13.130 --> 11:14.490
failed your aunt.

11:16.420 --> 11:18.010
She would never be angry with you.

11:18.580 --> 11:20.060
You are her closest

11:20.060 --> 11:21.010
and most trusted.

11:21.300 --> 11:23.300
Closer than Uncle Zhou,
closer than my parents.

11:23.300 --> 11:24.770
Your bond is steadfast, like kin.

11:25.180 --> 11:26.580
Mom's always been jealous of it.

11:28.610 --> 11:29.460
Besides,

11:30.180 --> 11:32.300
if Master hadn't gone to
Luoying Valley every year

11:32.300 --> 11:33.650
to heal her and sustain her life,

11:33.650 --> 11:34.530
wasting your inner power,

11:36.030 --> 11:38.060
how could you have been tricked
by villains so easily?

11:41.300 --> 11:42.650
What's the use of going every year?

11:43.610 --> 11:44.450
Your aunt...

11:45.420 --> 11:46.940
still left in the end.

11:50.980 --> 11:52.250
Master.

11:53.340 --> 11:54.770
Have you forgotten what aunt said?

11:55.180 --> 11:56.490
People come and go.

11:56.490 --> 11:57.650
It's all fate.

11:58.250 --> 11:59.250
No need to grieve.

12:00.610 --> 12:01.580
I understand.

12:03.130 --> 12:04.940
There's something I must ask you.

12:05.220 --> 12:06.120
About Chang Ning.

12:06.130 --> 12:07.130
Do you know where he went?

12:10.420 --> 12:11.850
He said he's tired of Jianghu,

12:12.150 --> 12:13.530
and retired to live as a wealthy man.

12:16.730 --> 12:17.570
Zhao,

12:17.770 --> 12:18.610
you're

12:18.980 --> 12:20.130
pure-hearted,

12:20.150 --> 12:21.250
and loyal to your loved ones.

12:21.250 --> 12:22.580
I don't oppose that,

12:23.130 --> 12:25.060
but the heart of man is unfathomable.

12:25.060 --> 12:26.220
It's hard to tell friend from foe.

12:26.850 --> 12:27.690
From now on,

12:27.790 --> 12:29.650
you must not leave the sect
without permission.

12:29.650 --> 12:31.300
Don't make your parents worry about you.

12:35.250 --> 12:36.090
And,

12:36.820 --> 12:38.100
don't mind I'm nagging.

12:39.130 --> 12:40.370
I'm just scared

12:41.530 --> 12:43.610
I can't protect you.

12:44.060 --> 12:45.530
Scared you'll end up like your aunt,

12:46.060 --> 12:47.580
stubborn and gone forever.

12:50.650 --> 12:52.130
The struggle has lasted for 100 years,

12:52.580 --> 12:53.890
causing countless blood feuds.

12:54.180 --> 12:55.700
One wrong step

12:56.370 --> 12:58.250
can lead to eternal damnation.

12:58.700 --> 12:59.540
Do you understand?

13:02.100 --> 13:02.940
I do.

13:04.700 --> 13:05.540
Come.

13:34.850 --> 13:37.530
Has Master guessed
Chang Ning's identity?

13:41.980 --> 13:43.730
Fine, I won't meddle.

13:43.940 --> 13:44.780
I'm busy right now.

13:45.730 --> 13:47.700
My Golden Silk Armor is launching soon.

13:48.180 --> 13:49.340
I have to manage the shops

13:50.250 --> 13:51.490
and contact buyers.

14:05.250 --> 14:06.090
(Zhao.)

14:06.220 --> 14:07.610
(Have you been well?)

14:07.850 --> 14:09.010
(Dad came back and said)

14:09.220 --> 14:10.530
(Ning has left.)

14:10.820 --> 14:12.420
(Where did he go?)

14:12.700 --> 14:13.980
(I'm so worried about him.)

14:14.300 --> 14:15.530
(How is his wound now?)

14:15.890 --> 14:18.420
(I only eat vegetarian food
at Grandma's home.)

14:18.580 --> 14:20.700
(I feel like I'm turning into a sheep.)

14:21.010 --> 14:23.890
(I really crave Ning's wontons.)

14:24.320 --> 14:25.770
(The taste still lingers on my lips.)

14:26.220 --> 14:28.460
(My mouth is watering.)

14:28.770 --> 14:32.610
(Where else can I find wontons
that delicious?)

14:32.820 --> 14:35.490
(I should have made him
write down the recipe.)

14:37.620 --> 14:42.610
♪You come to my dreams again♪

14:43.940 --> 14:49.970
♪On this cold day, drunk with wine♪

14:51.940 --> 14:58.690
♪Life shifts, a thousand faces pass by♪

14:59.300 --> 15:04.850
♪Yet I never forget yours♪

15:06.470 --> 15:12.120
♪Beneath the stars,
I await the rising sun♪

15:12.760 --> 15:19.730
♪Across rivers and mountains,
I roam free and wide♪

15:20.630 --> 15:27.480
♪All the youth and bliss simply
could be boiled down to a toast♪

15:28.000 --> 15:32.750
♪Ten years of turmoil and sorrow
only could be lit up with a lamp♪

15:34.330 --> 15:40.580
♪Life passes in a blink♪

15:41.150 --> 15:44.810
♪Years grow long,
yet simple joys grow few♪

15:44.810 --> 15:48.840
♪Too many days lost♪

15:48.840 --> 15:53.030
♪How many lovers♪

15:53.030 --> 15:56.600
♪Once stood side by side
through hardships♪

15:56.600 --> 15:58.050
♪In the end♪

15:59.980 --> 16:02.530
I once promised Ning I'd protect you.

16:03.700 --> 16:05.250
Never let you face this alone,

16:05.550 --> 16:06.490
or let you seek revenge.

16:06.580 --> 16:08.300
Now I'm afraid
I have to break that promise.

16:08.980 --> 16:09.820
Zhao, rest assured.

16:11.100 --> 16:12.370
I will avenge the Chang Fort.

16:13.060 --> 16:13.900
Avenge my father.

16:14.940 --> 16:15.850
Avenge myself.

16:17.770 --> 16:19.060
Once I return to the Li Sect,

16:20.220 --> 16:21.460
I will tear Nie Zhe

16:21.700 --> 16:23.010
and the Demonic Camp

16:24.460 --> 16:25.770
limb from limb.

16:27.080 --> 16:33.720
♪For you, I guard the fading lamp♪

16:45.220 --> 16:46.060
You didn't leave.

16:46.610 --> 16:47.850
The Smiley spilled everywhere.

16:49.300 --> 16:50.340
You owe me a new pouch.

16:51.060 --> 16:53.490
The Snow Mountain is at least
a thousand li from here.

16:53.610 --> 16:55.850
Even if you ride nonstop,
no food, no rest,

16:55.910 --> 16:57.340
it'll take you dozens of days
to get there.

16:57.490 --> 16:58.890
Why not take my Golden Peng?

16:59.220 --> 17:00.580
You'll arrive in two days.

17:09.250 --> 17:10.180
You rascal.

17:10.180 --> 17:11.140
You're alive.

17:11.710 --> 17:12.650
You were waiting for me.

17:13.010 --> 17:13.940
How could I dare die?

17:41.220 --> 17:42.460
Mr. Mu!

17:45.770 --> 17:46.610
Mr. Mu.

17:46.770 --> 17:47.660
This place of yours

17:47.770 --> 17:49.660
was so hard for me to find.

17:49.750 --> 17:51.250
If someone hadn't led the way outside,

17:51.380 --> 17:52.330
I would have...

17:53.460 --> 17:56.700
I would have never
seen you again, Mr. Mu.

17:57.420 --> 17:58.530
My father loved peace,

17:59.140 --> 18:00.460
hated being disturbed.

18:01.290 --> 18:03.730
So he set up a Deadly Formation
outside the Carefree.

18:05.380 --> 18:06.530
Does that mean I

18:06.700 --> 18:08.770
can't gaze upon Mr. Mu's face every day,

18:08.770 --> 18:10.620
and hear your teachings?

18:10.940 --> 18:13.460
I can have someone teach you
how to break the formation.

18:13.900 --> 18:15.660
Thank you, Mr. Mu.

18:15.660 --> 18:16.770
What have you found?

18:17.550 --> 18:19.380
All altars and strongholds
are sealed off.

18:19.380 --> 18:20.250
No one in, only out.

18:20.620 --> 18:22.700
Fearing I'd alert the enemy

18:22.700 --> 18:23.940
and ruin your grand plan, Mr. Mu,

18:24.050 --> 18:27.570
I haven't found where the corpse slaves
are being forged yet.

18:29.490 --> 18:30.660
Keep investigating.

18:32.900 --> 18:33.740
Yes.

18:40.900 --> 18:41.740
Mr. Mu.

18:42.330 --> 18:43.220
Can he be trusted?

18:43.940 --> 18:45.570
Trust doesn't matter.

18:46.380 --> 18:48.420
As long as he's useful to me.

19:03.140 --> 19:04.730
(He hasn't killed Nie Zhe yet.)

19:04.910 --> 19:06.220
(His vengeance remains unavenged.)

19:06.570 --> 19:07.730
(So he surely won't die.)

19:07.730 --> 19:08.860
Zhao!

19:10.010 --> 19:10.900
Zhao.

19:12.420 --> 19:13.980
I've found 30 shops.

19:14.180 --> 19:17.090
Once the Golden Silk Soft Armor
hits the market, it'll stun the Jianghu.

19:17.370 --> 19:18.330
It'll spread everywhere.

19:18.730 --> 19:21.010
Good. With Xingjia handling it,
I'm at ease.

19:24.380 --> 19:25.220
Zhao.

19:25.320 --> 19:27.010
You've seemed troubled
these past few days.

19:33.860 --> 19:35.330
I can't help but feel uneasy.

19:35.810 --> 19:37.050
What makes you uneasy?

19:41.050 --> 19:42.730
There was a fluffy little duckling.

19:44.180 --> 19:45.020
Cute-looking.

19:45.390 --> 19:46.490
But with a terrible temper.

19:47.010 --> 19:48.250
After I raised it for a while,

19:48.920 --> 19:50.460
I realized it wasn't a duckling at all.

19:51.220 --> 19:53.090
It was a proud white goose.

19:54.050 --> 19:54.940
Fine, it was a goose.

19:55.090 --> 19:56.860
But he insists on
venturing into the world.

19:59.460 --> 20:00.730
I'm a bit uneasy about it.

20:01.340 --> 20:02.730
I fear he might get caught and roasted.

20:08.090 --> 20:08.930
You...

20:09.230 --> 20:10.490
Don't tell me you're eyeing Master Lei's

20:10.500 --> 20:11.700
ducks.

20:12.180 --> 20:13.490
Please, don't.

20:13.940 --> 20:15.330
If you touch Master Lei's ducks,

20:15.330 --> 20:16.660
he'll kill you.

20:26.660 --> 20:27.500
Zhao!

20:27.660 --> 20:29.050
I'll buy you one tomorrow!

20:29.050 --> 20:30.530
Don't do anything impulsive!

20:42.380 --> 20:43.220
Hold out your hand.

20:46.140 --> 20:47.050
Uncle Lei,

20:47.460 --> 20:48.980
I've fully recovered already.

20:49.250 --> 20:51.050
No need for any more
follow-ups now, right?

20:57.680 --> 20:58.700
Who are you worried about?

21:01.010 --> 21:01.860
Uncle Lei,

21:03.090 --> 21:04.460
you're truly extraordinary.

21:05.220 --> 21:06.810
I'm worried anyone could sense it.

21:07.380 --> 21:08.570
Your pulse is thin and taut.

21:08.810 --> 21:10.050
Dark circles beneath the eyes.

21:10.490 --> 21:11.660
Restless through the night.

21:12.530 --> 21:13.660
Too troubled to sleep.

21:15.270 --> 21:16.660
You're worried about Chang Ning, right?

21:19.790 --> 21:21.770
He's down the mountain
feasting and drinking richly.

21:22.090 --> 21:23.220
Why should I worry about him?

21:23.330 --> 21:24.490
Feasting and drinking richly.

21:25.390 --> 21:26.380
That boy has a hard fate.

21:27.860 --> 21:30.140
One day he might die somewhere,
with no one knowing.

21:31.460 --> 21:32.300
What do you mean?

21:32.580 --> 21:33.770
What do you mean "die somewhere"?

21:34.420 --> 21:35.380
The poison in his body

21:35.620 --> 21:36.810
wasn't completely removed.

21:36.890 --> 21:38.070
But his martial arts and inner power

21:38.080 --> 21:39.250
have all recovered, haven't they?

21:40.330 --> 21:41.180
By reason,

21:42.320 --> 21:44.010
the poison shouldn't be
severe now, right?

21:44.320 --> 21:45.300
It's not that it isn't severe.

21:46.380 --> 21:47.250
But it's quite severe.

21:49.220 --> 21:50.140
Incurable.

22:01.290 --> 22:02.660
He looked perfectly fine,

22:03.290 --> 22:04.980
and fought harder than me.

22:11.180 --> 22:12.860
Uncle Lei,

22:13.330 --> 22:15.770
they say you're the greatest
Divine Healer in the world.

22:15.900 --> 22:17.180
Isn't there any way

22:17.290 --> 22:18.490
to cure his injury?

22:18.830 --> 22:21.460
The impurities in his vital energy
and viscera have been drawn out,

22:22.180 --> 22:23.380
but beneath the meridians,

22:24.010 --> 22:25.620
a strange poison still lingers.

22:25.760 --> 22:27.050
One I've never seen in my life.

22:27.060 --> 22:28.460
Even with all my
acupuncture and medicine,

22:28.980 --> 22:29.860
there's no cure.

22:30.730 --> 22:32.290
I've warned him countless times before.

22:32.770 --> 22:34.530
If one day he were gravely wounded,

22:34.770 --> 22:36.140
or pushed his inner force too far,

22:37.330 --> 22:39.700
his meridians might rupture
and claim his life.

22:41.860 --> 22:42.700
That fool…

22:43.250 --> 22:44.490
He's always trying to be tough.

22:44.980 --> 22:46.180
Perhaps he himself

22:46.490 --> 22:47.860
knows his days are numbered,

22:48.250 --> 22:49.620
and he's set on revenge,

22:50.700 --> 22:51.940
so he left alone and resolute.

22:52.430 --> 22:53.810
You two were together day and night

22:55.180 --> 22:56.900
and you never noticed anything?

22:57.700 --> 22:58.700
I'll never let anyone

22:58.700 --> 23:00.090
lock me up again.

23:00.530 --> 23:01.570
Maybe it won't be long

23:02.570 --> 23:04.290
before you're relieved of your worry.

23:07.900 --> 23:08.740
Uncle Lei,

23:10.090 --> 23:11.290
how much longer can he live?

23:11.290 --> 23:13.660
He's barely sustained
by medicine right now.

23:14.770 --> 23:16.090
Maybe a few years.

23:16.660 --> 23:17.730
Maybe a few months.

23:18.380 --> 23:19.220
I originally

23:19.530 --> 23:21.090
prepared a medicinal incense for him

23:22.180 --> 23:23.090
which could save his life

23:23.330 --> 23:24.250
in a pinch.

23:26.620 --> 23:27.490
It's a pity

23:33.730 --> 23:34.570
he's already gone.

23:34.580 --> 23:35.860
You don't have to worry anymore.

23:37.470 --> 23:38.810
Your master is entering seclusion again.

23:39.180 --> 23:40.570
I've prepared some medicinal herbs.

23:41.220 --> 23:42.330
Please help me deliver them.

23:47.620 --> 23:50.620
(Chang Ning)

24:05.900 --> 24:07.820
(Chang Ning)

24:17.660 --> 24:18.620
By reason,

24:19.940 --> 24:21.330
the poison shouldn't be
severe now, right?

24:21.620 --> 24:22.610
It's not that it isn't severe.

24:23.420 --> 24:24.330
But it's quite severe.

24:25.620 --> 24:26.460
Incurable.

24:27.550 --> 24:29.620
One day he might die somewhere,
with no one knowing.

24:30.380 --> 24:31.220
Young Master said

24:31.620 --> 24:32.770
he can't let you

24:32.770 --> 24:34.380
be alone and helpless outside,

24:34.580 --> 24:37.050
can't let you risk your life
at the Snow Mountain by yourself.

24:37.380 --> 24:38.860
I am already a dying man.

24:39.720 --> 24:40.770
If I live and can't avenge,

24:40.770 --> 24:41.860
I might as well die.

24:42.460 --> 24:45.420
(Chang Ning)

25:16.920 --> 25:18.050
Just bring him some medicine.

25:18.180 --> 25:19.730
I'll never expose my identity.

25:19.980 --> 25:21.380
If he's missing
this life-saving medicine,

25:21.620 --> 25:23.140
fails to avenge
and dies with regret,

25:23.340 --> 25:25.330
that petty man will surely
become a vengeful ghost

25:25.570 --> 25:26.730
and haunt me every day,

25:26.730 --> 25:27.860
saying I'm ungrateful.

25:30.180 --> 25:31.140
Zhao.

25:32.660 --> 25:33.620
Yuzhi.

25:35.050 --> 25:35.940
It's getting late.

25:35.940 --> 25:37.330
Whatever it is, let's talk tomorrow.

25:37.570 --> 25:38.460
I need to rest now.

25:38.620 --> 25:40.120
So you've truly made up your mind

25:40.130 --> 25:41.050
to go to the demon sect?

26:03.020 --> 26:03.940
Yuzhi, mind your words.

26:04.770 --> 26:06.490
I'm a disciple of a righteous sect.

26:06.660 --> 26:08.220
Why would I ever go to the demon sect?

26:08.660 --> 26:10.050
You're going to find Chang Ning,

26:10.730 --> 26:12.330
and Chang Ning is Mr. Mu.

26:12.330 --> 26:14.330
You managed to get the saliva
so easily last time,

26:14.430 --> 26:16.490
surely his help had something
to do with it, right?

26:16.980 --> 26:18.810
Luoying Valley never forgets kindness.

26:18.810 --> 26:20.380
If he were safe and sound,
it would be fine,

26:20.380 --> 26:21.900
but now he's at death's door.

26:22.250 --> 26:23.860
You must be going to repay his favor.

26:24.860 --> 26:25.860
I suppose

26:25.860 --> 26:27.620
you've even packed your things.

26:29.100 --> 26:30.060
(Chang Ning)

26:36.860 --> 26:38.570
Yuzhi, if you want to snitch on me,

26:39.700 --> 26:41.090
then let's settle it with a duel.

26:43.860 --> 26:44.940
I'm going with you.

26:45.720 --> 26:47.010
Last time, I was healing,

26:47.010 --> 26:48.530
forcing you to risk your life alone.

26:48.980 --> 26:50.290
This time I ought to go with you,

26:50.290 --> 26:51.420
to protect you.

26:51.570 --> 26:52.460
Besides,

26:52.700 --> 26:55.290
I need to borrow the Jade Sunflower
from Mr. Mu.

26:55.490 --> 26:56.530
No, no.

26:57.010 --> 26:58.250
If you go with me,

26:58.250 --> 26:59.860
Lingbo will definitely hunt me down.

27:00.330 --> 27:02.090
I'll get the Jade Sunflower for you.

27:02.090 --> 27:03.810
Do you know how to
get to the Youming Path?

27:08.270 --> 27:10.490
This is a route map I found
by looking through ancient texts.

27:13.700 --> 27:15.810
It can help you avoid
many eerie caves along the way.

27:15.810 --> 27:17.050
(Youming Path)
Straight to demon sect.

27:19.700 --> 27:20.660
(Yichou)

27:20.860 --> 27:21.700
Yichou?

27:22.660 --> 27:24.770
This map is from sixteen years ago.

27:24.920 --> 27:25.900
Can it still be accurate?

27:29.140 --> 27:30.220
I'll cover all expenses.

27:34.330 --> 27:35.190
No need.

27:35.190 --> 27:36.380
I still have some savings of my own.

27:39.910 --> 27:42.180
The defense of Qingque Sect
will also be my responsibility.

27:42.180 --> 27:43.220
If I don't go with you,

27:43.220 --> 27:45.090
you won't even
get past the Thousandfold Cliff.

27:45.700 --> 27:46.570
Besides,

27:46.570 --> 27:47.420
with me by your side,

27:47.420 --> 27:49.860
you won't be accused of
colluding with the demon sect.

27:51.660 --> 27:52.900
Then if I go with you,

27:54.050 --> 27:56.570
I won't be accused of that?

27:56.610 --> 27:57.460
You won't.

27:57.460 --> 27:58.300
Why?

28:01.700 --> 28:02.540
Right.

28:02.810 --> 28:03.770
They'll only suspect me,

28:03.770 --> 28:05.140
never you.

28:05.380 --> 28:07.050
Comparing people
only breeds frustration.

28:08.980 --> 28:09.820
No time to waste.

28:09.940 --> 28:10.860
Let's set out now.

28:10.860 --> 28:12.860
Milady, Yuzhi!

28:13.090 --> 28:15.570
You can't elope!

28:17.860 --> 28:18.820
(Lunar Gleam)
Elope?

28:19.140 --> 28:20.090
Why would you elope?

28:20.090 --> 28:21.010
Exactly.

28:21.290 --> 28:22.250
Do I look that idle?

28:22.810 --> 28:23.700
Milady.

28:24.050 --> 28:25.530
If it's not eloping,

28:25.530 --> 28:27.990
then why is a man and a woman
alone on a bed late at night,

28:28.000 --> 28:29.850
plotting to go down the mountain?

28:30.090 --> 28:32.620
Ning is in trouble down the mountain.

28:32.830 --> 28:34.770
We're planning to go help him.

28:34.770 --> 28:36.530
Then why not tell Master directly

28:36.530 --> 28:37.990
and ask for his help?

28:38.810 --> 28:40.090
Master's old wound hasn't healed.

28:40.320 --> 28:42.330
Things on the mountain
have only just calmed down.

28:42.530 --> 28:44.180
We don't want to trouble his mind.

28:45.140 --> 28:45.980
Besides…

28:45.990 --> 28:48.180
Chang Fort has shown great kindness
to our Luoying Valley.

28:49.940 --> 28:51.140
How could we turn a blind eye?

28:51.290 --> 28:52.130
Milady.

28:52.770 --> 28:54.050
Go and come back quickly.

28:54.530 --> 28:55.370
Rest assured.

28:55.730 --> 28:57.050
I'll come back as soon as I'm done.

28:58.090 --> 28:59.710
Wait, don't go yet.

29:02.660 --> 29:03.990
Can you tell me the truth?

29:04.140 --> 29:05.780
Are you heading to the demon sect?

29:11.290 --> 29:13.290
Though the demon sect is in turmoil now,

29:13.460 --> 29:15.460
it's still not easy to sneak in.

29:15.570 --> 29:16.860
Go persuade Chang,

29:17.220 --> 29:19.140
tell him not to be in such a hurry
to take revenge.

29:22.960 --> 29:24.800
I'll pass on Xingjia's words

29:25.000 --> 29:26.290
to Chang.

29:26.530 --> 29:28.090
Yuzhi,

29:28.220 --> 29:29.570
you can set out with Zhao at ease.

29:29.650 --> 29:31.180
Xiaolan and I will handle things here.

29:39.210 --> 29:40.140
Zhao,

29:40.660 --> 29:41.830
where are we going?

29:42.450 --> 29:44.530
Hanhai Mountains are on the other side.

29:45.030 --> 29:46.250
Come with me to meet someone first.

29:46.470 --> 29:47.810
He must have the latest route map.

29:48.730 --> 29:49.570
Alright.

29:57.530 --> 29:59.530
The Young Master
ordered me to wait here,

30:00.220 --> 30:02.420
so that Miss Cai wouldn't
venture into danger.

30:02.810 --> 30:05.810
Hanhai Mountains are perilous now.

30:06.140 --> 30:09.250
I cannot risk
handing over the route map.

30:09.280 --> 30:11.290
Mu Qingyan already knows
I plan to descend the mountain?

30:13.730 --> 30:14.940
How is he lately?

30:17.230 --> 30:18.860
The Young Master
is masterminding everything.

30:18.860 --> 30:20.090
He's doing fine.

30:21.290 --> 30:22.130
Sir.

30:23.220 --> 30:25.140
What's the current situation
in the Li Sect?

30:26.570 --> 30:27.620
Miss Cai.

30:27.980 --> 30:28.860
Who is he?

30:29.460 --> 30:30.900
This is my Third Senior Brother.

30:30.900 --> 30:31.740
Song Yuzhi.

30:33.810 --> 30:34.730
Mr. Pig?

30:36.290 --> 30:37.900
Song Yuzhi, surname Song.

30:40.700 --> 30:43.250
Everyone in the Li Sect
serves under the Young Master.

30:43.400 --> 30:44.530
All is well there.

30:44.860 --> 30:46.000
Mr. Pig.

30:46.420 --> 30:47.260
Have some tea.

30:48.810 --> 30:49.730
He's

30:49.730 --> 30:51.140
Mr. Song.

30:51.940 --> 30:52.980
The Hanhai Mountains

30:52.980 --> 30:54.050
stretch for a thousand li.

30:54.050 --> 30:55.250
Filled with countless traps.

30:55.250 --> 30:56.380
Without a guide,

30:56.700 --> 30:59.180
you'll never make it into the Li Sect.

30:59.810 --> 31:02.090
Please leave after you finish your tea.

31:02.190 --> 31:04.220
Mu Qingyan promised to
take responsibility for me.

31:04.380 --> 31:05.860
Now he's turning his back on me?

31:07.250 --> 31:08.180
Take...

31:08.180 --> 31:09.810
Such a big matter.

31:10.010 --> 31:11.730
I'm just a servant,
I can't make that call.

31:12.460 --> 31:14.380
When the Young Master secures his place,

31:14.810 --> 31:16.810
he will surely give you an explanation.

31:17.900 --> 31:18.900
I has other business,

31:19.230 --> 31:20.250
so I'll take my leave now.

31:33.540 --> 31:35.290
Even making wontons
counts as taking responsibility.

31:35.380 --> 31:36.330
I'm not lying.

31:41.220 --> 31:42.090
Zhao.

31:42.090 --> 31:42.930
Look.

31:44.770 --> 31:46.010
Could it be a route map?

31:50.660 --> 31:51.900
A safety talisman?

31:58.990 --> 32:00.290
We can't just come here for nothing.

32:26.460 --> 32:27.420
Mu Qingyan!

32:28.140 --> 32:29.860
You chose to come back
and die on your own.

32:30.180 --> 32:31.700
Chief ordered us to fulfill your wish.

32:32.330 --> 32:33.250
Mr. Mu.

32:33.250 --> 32:34.420
Chief is merciful.

32:34.830 --> 32:35.730
Why not

32:35.730 --> 32:37.490
end the hostility and make peace?

32:37.620 --> 32:38.730
Let's talk it over.

32:38.730 --> 32:39.570
Master You,

32:40.660 --> 32:42.140
you wanted to gaze upon my face,

32:42.660 --> 32:43.900
and hear my teachings.

32:44.530 --> 32:45.700
Why bring so many people here?

32:46.700 --> 32:47.770
To listen together?

32:49.620 --> 32:50.460
Master You,

32:50.720 --> 32:52.420
I'll give you a chance
to redeem yourself.

32:52.770 --> 32:54.380
Go take down that man named Mu.

32:54.940 --> 32:56.730
I'll commend you to the strategist.

33:17.620 --> 33:18.490
Kill him!

33:41.570 --> 33:42.410
Go!

33:51.980 --> 33:53.420
Master You, do you want to save Xing?

33:59.120 --> 34:09.780
=Generation to Generation=

34:28.540 --> 34:32.950
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

34:33.515 --> 34:38.130
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

34:38.470 --> 34:43.035
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

34:43.560 --> 34:47.860
♪Free to wander in the world♪

34:50.805 --> 34:55.505
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

34:56.030 --> 35:00.320
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

35:00.980 --> 35:05.010
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

35:05.325 --> 35:10.450
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

35:11.025 --> 35:15.835
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

35:16.050 --> 35:20.220
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

35:20.945 --> 35:24.880
♪I freely roam in the world♪

35:25.380 --> 35:30.655
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

35:53.385 --> 35:58.515
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

35:58.880 --> 36:03.250
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

36:03.515 --> 36:07.645
♪I freely roam in the world♪

36:07.830 --> 36:13.405
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
